translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 死んだ方がマシってえくらいのキツい罰だ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's such a harsh punishment that death would be better!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 逆らう馬鹿はどういう目に遭うか教えてやらぁ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll teach fools who defy me what they'll face!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうすりゃあ、皆それで分かるだろう！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That way, everyone will understand!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「本当に慕い愛すべき男が誰なのか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Who is the man they should truly adore and love!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、そうだ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, that's right!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺を愛さねえ連中なら何したって構わねえ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don't care what happens to those who don't love me!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最初からそうするべきだったんだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I should have done that from the start!
...No, I don't.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぽつりと、ケイブリスの笑い声で
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Quietly, Kayblis's laughter

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 埋め尽くされていた部屋に声が落とされる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: fell upon the room that had been completely filled.
...Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 声の主は、ケイブリスとの戦いに敗れてレイプされ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The voice belonged to Camilla, who had been defeated and raped by Kayblis,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ボロボロになり床に転がっていたカミーラ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: completely battered and lying on the floor.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゾッとするほどの美貌の持ち主が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: An owner of terrifyingly stunning beauty,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今は全身を白濁の液体にまみれさせていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: was now covered from head to toe in a milky-white liquid.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、それでも、目だけは死んでない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, even then, her eyes were not dead.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まるで刀のように、冷たく鋭い。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They were cold and sharp, like a blade.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「確かにお前は強くなった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You have certainly become stronger...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だが、その性根は何も変わっていない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But the core of your nature hasn't changed at all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「地面を這いつくばり、穴を掘り……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Crawling on the ground, digging holes...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コソコソとしているのがお似合いの……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sneaking around suits you...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうしようもなく、情けない……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pathetically hopeless...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ムシケラだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...You’re just a bug.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まだほざくかァァアァアアァ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Still babbling, huhhhh!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ううぐっ……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスに上から踏まれ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Stepped on by Kayblis from above,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カミーラが苦悶に満ちた声を上げた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Camilla let out a voice full of agony.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「この野郎！　この野郎！　この野郎！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You bastard! You bastard! You bastard!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 本当はその体引き千切りまくりてぇが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I really want to tear that body apart...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それじゃあ苦痛が一瞬だ……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But that would make the pain only momentary...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いいかァ！？　てめぇは絶対に殺さねぇからな！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Listen up! I'm never going to kill you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この先もずぅぅぅぅぅっとお前の大嫌いな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From now on, forever, the one you hate most,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様のそばに置き続けてやる！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll keep you right by my side!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どうだ！？　悔しいか！？　悔しいだろう！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How about that!? Are you frustrated!? You're frustrated, right!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ざまぁみろ！！！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Serves you right!!!!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、そうだ！　そしてだなぁ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, that's right! And another thing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様はお前の愛も手に入れるぜェ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll also get your love!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 絶対の絶対の絶対にだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Absolutely, absolutely, absolutely!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「オラ！　愛してるわケイブリス様って言いやがれ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on! Say 'I love you, Lord Kayblis!'!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どんだけ殴ればテメェはそう言うんだァ！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How many times do I have to hit you before you say it!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言え！　言うんだよ！　言えっつってんだろうが！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Say it! Say it! I told you to say it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「言いやがれェエェエェあぁ゛ぁあ゛ぁ゛ぁ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Say it alreadyaaahhh!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「アッ！　アアァァァ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah! Aaaah!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 更に体重をかけて踏まれ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He pressed down with even more weight,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 肺の中の酸素が全て声と共に吐き出される。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: all the oxygen in her lungs was expelled with her voice.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その拍子に膣内に注ぎ込まれた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At that moment, what had been poured into her vagina

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 白濁色の精液がゴポリと溢れるのを見て、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: overflowed with a gurgling sound, and seeing that,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスが爛々と瞳を輝かせる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kayblis's eyes gleamed brightly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぐ、ぐふ、ぐふふ……そうか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: G-guh, guhuhu... I see...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まぁぁだ、俺様の愛が足りてねぇようだな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems my love still isn't enough...
